## 📣 PILLAR 6: MARKETING & GROWTH

### Automated Messages
- **24hr Reminder** — *"Your appointment is tomorrow at 3pm"*
- **2hr Reminder** — *"See you in 2 hours!"*
- **Thank You** — Sent 1hr after appointment
- **Re-engagement** — *"We miss you!"* after 45/60/90 days

### Email Campaigns
- Beautiful salon-branded templates
- Send to all clients, VIPs only, or inactive clients
- Campaign analytics: open rate, click rate

### SMS Campaigns
- Bulk promo SMS with opt-out management
- *"Flash Sale! 20% off all color services this weekend"*

### Social Media Integration
- Auto-post: *"✨ Fresh cut by Ali at Velvet Rose! Book now"*
- Instagram feed embedded on booking page
- Share booking confirmation on Instagram story

### Referral Program
- Client gets unique referral link
- Friend books → Both get $10 credit
- Referral leaderboard

### Google Business Integration
- Sync hours, photos, services to Google Business Profile
- "Book Now" button directly on Google listing
- Review management — reply to Google reviews from dashboard

