## 📋 DEVELOPMENT PHASES

### ✅ Phase 0 — Current (DONE)
AI Voice, Dashboard, Booking, Payments, Multi-tenant, Email/SMS

### 🔄 Phase 1 — Launch Ready (Month 1-2)
Edge Functions, Online Booking Page, Automated Reminders, Reports, Payment Expiry

### 📈 Phase 2 — Growth (Month 3-4)
Client CRM, Calendar Sync, Promo Codes, Commission Tracking, Client Notes

### 🚀 Phase 3 — Premium (Month 5-8)
WhatsApp AI, Website Builder, POS, Loyalty Program, Mobile App

### 🌍 Phase 4 — Enterprise (Month 9-12)
Multi-Location, Client App, Franchise Mode, API, Marketplace

